			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="1. WYR, Sharess Caress, RAphael's room&#xD;&#xA;2. Make deal with Raphael&#xD;&#xA;3. Teleport to LOW, HoH&#xD;&#xA;4. Teleport to Incubus, kill him, loot his key&#xD;&#xA;5. Open big painting on the wall behind him. Loot and read note.&#xD;&#xA;6. Teleport to Archivist.&#xD;&#xA;7. Click on big barrel with contract. Choose the password you read on the note.&#xD;&#xA;8. Take contract. Interact with it in inventory" />
			<attribute id="needLayout" type="bool" value="False" />
